{"tid":653841,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：無印Cafe","createTime":"2018-05-05T05:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T00:09:49.000Z","uid":181719,"like":22,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9643effa565fb6f6d491b9673398b52c27e85539","tid":653841,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"尖咀無印又係我飯堂之一黎，貪佢水準keep到之餘，又有吧檯毒毒地食。基本上每次去親都係食個4點拼盤，即係2涼菜2熱盤拼湯同飯嘅套餐。110蚊試到咁多野，都算係咁。但係今次去，真係差咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/134937_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F134937_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0613f0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先講涼菜，厚燒玉子之前食過幾次都好好食，但今次煮老咗，口感好鞋，又冇咗我至愛嘅明太子醬，乾得滯，比較劣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/135003_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F135003_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=10a3465c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一碟涼菜帶子沙律，汁微酸，開胃嘅，但帶子肉質偏韌，又得2小粒，稍為孤寒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/135029_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F135029_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=af87f2ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱盤我揀咗汁煮牛肋肉同比目魚2款。牛肉唔係無印應有水準黎，又係煮老咗。加上呢款汁淡口，應該襯到比較濃嘅牛肉味，結果都係唔得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/135244_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F135244_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=82044b75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比目魚已經係成餐飯最好食果樣野。魚肉密度高，咬感良好而且完全唔腥，但呢啲係比目魚嘅先天優勢黎，唔係佢煮法得別出色，所以結論都只係中上啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/05/135314_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F05%2F135314_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8d5b201b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實無印嘅疏乎厘班戟係好好食，但係今次一支公食唔到，希望下次去食嘅時候，4點拼盤可以振作番啲！"},{"pid":"e241a0a1c5555d5a1bc954113ac3f7f80a1b70da","tid":653841,"uid":60000,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:54:24.000Z","msg":"好貴"},{"pid":"b4f36a67d41b3f5af5e4f7ae241055bac59baffc","tid":653841,"uid":158337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51709e127a404789b0c32ed6078f78f6c5c538d6","tid":653841,"uid":181719,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"e241a0a1c5555d5a1bc954113ac3f7f80a1b70da","tid":653841,"uid":60000,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:54:24.000Z","msg":"好貴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:08:40.000Z","msg":"我覺得其他野真係貴，但呢個set百頭試到多野又ok<br />\n疏乎厘班戟真係要試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb77b31c9d3ca9b775f56c8c077c3cb42d5b73e","tid":653841,"uid":181719,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4f36a67d41b3f5af5e4f7ae241055bac59baffc","tid":653841,"uid":158337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T05:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝收睇"},{"pid":"c87b3bbad4d4bae30c6e7d40519079e55a0da0a6","tid":653841,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T06:10:17.000Z","msg":"夠唔夠飽架<img src=\"/as